commit.message: fix:  Fixed a bug that prevented finding nested subfiles
Avoid introducing breaks into fixed abbreviations such as i.e. or e.g. (Partially) fixes #269
Refactor: arrange order of constituent definitions for pattern definition
remove duplicated braces
improved processing of Chinese and Japanese texts in that splitting is done based on characters.  Fixes #229, fixes #145 (credit belongs to git user LuXu)
Correct prior commit with faulty comment
Add \begin and \end as UNSAFEMATHCMD. Remove split from MATHARRENV. Fixes #258. Fixes #109
Make links to external programs clickable in manual, update link. Fixes #223
Change install syntax in Makefile for increased portability. Fixes #230
--flatten now works for empty files. Fixes issue #242
Improved processing for FINE math markup mode.  (Partially) fixes #235  #244
Replace deleted equation arrays with their starred variants instead of a generic default
In WHOLE and COARSE math modes, now properly treat math environments with arguments such as \alignat. Fixes #251
